WEBVTT

00:10.810 --> 00:12.175
[dish clatters]

00:19.680 --> 00:21.011
SHAWN.

00:21.820 --> 00:23.515
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HOME
FROM SCHOOL?

00:24.690 --> 00:25.645
UH...

00:25.690 --> 00:28.409
UH, WELL...

00:28.460 --> 00:31.827
AT THE ASSEMBLY TODAY,
THERE WAS A GUY.

00:31.860 --> 00:34.192
AND HE HYPNOTIZED
SOME STUDENTS.

00:34.230 --> 00:36.790
AND ONE OF THEM THOUGHT
HE WAS A KANGAROO.

00:36.830 --> 00:38.127
AND HE PUNCHED THE GUY.

00:38.170 --> 00:39.091
AND HE PASSED OUT

00:39.140 --> 00:41.199
BEFORE HE COULD PUT THE KIDS
BACK TO NORMAL.

00:41.240 --> 00:42.138
UH, BUT LUCKILY,

00:42.170 --> 00:45.059
MR. DETMER,
AN EX-NAW SEAL,

00:45.110 --> 00:46.008
PUT EVERYONE BACK

00:46.040 --> 00:49.498
BEFORE SIX KIDS HAD TO GO
TO THE HOSPITAL.

00:49.550 --> 00:52.439
LET ME SEE THE SUSPENSION NOTE
FROM THE TEACHER.

00:52.480 --> 00:54.141
HOW DID YOU KNOW?

00:54.180 --> 00:55.340
KID, I GOT A NICKNAME
AT WORK.

00:55.380 --> 00:56.847
IT'S "THE HUMAN LIE
DETECTOR."

00:56.890 --> 00:59.188
I SPEND MY DAY
ANALYZING LIES

00:59.220 --> 01:00.653
AND THE PEOPLE
WHO TELL THEM.

01:00.690 --> 01:02.385
RULE NUMBER ONE.

01:02.430 --> 01:05.388
EVERY LIE IS BUILT
ON A KERNEL OF TRUTH.

01:05.430 --> 01:08.194
TAKE YOUR LITTLE FIB,
FOR INSTANCE.

01:08.230 --> 01:09.527
IF I WERE TO PUT MONEY
ON IT,

01:09.570 --> 01:11.094
I'D SAY THE ONLY TRUE THING
THAT YOU JUST SAID

01:11.130 --> 01:13.792
IS THAT MR. DETMER
IS EX-NAW SEAL.

01:13.840 --> 01:15.296
YOU'RE RIGHT.
THAT'S AMAZING.

01:15.340 --> 01:16.568
NOT REALLY.

01:16.610 --> 01:18.100
THE RELATIVE SPECIFICITY
OF THAT STATEMENT

01:18.140 --> 01:20.370
COMPARED TO THE OTHERS
MADE IT OBVIOUS.

01:20.410 --> 01:22.446
[refrigerator door
opens and closes]

01:22.480 --> 01:25.369
LOOK, SHAWN,
IF YOU CONTINUE

01:25.410 --> 01:27.241
TO LIE LIKE THIS,

01:27.280 --> 01:29.111
NOBODY'S GONNA BELIEVE YOU
WHEN IT COUNTS.

01:29.150 --> 01:31.209
AND THAT COULD PUT YOUR LIFE
ON THE LINE.

01:31.250 --> 01:34.151
LIKE MAYBE WHEN I
MIGHT BE A COP?

01:34.190 --> 01:36.249
NO. LIKE NOW.

01:38.430 --> 01:42.298
SHAWN SPENCER THRIVES
ON CLUTCH MOMENTS LIKE THIS.

01:43.430 --> 01:46.729
IT'S JUST HIM, THE BALL,
AND THE HOLE,

01:46.770 --> 01:48.658
SURROUNDED BY SILENCE.

01:48.700 --> 01:51.464
AND A MAN WEARING
A HEFI'Y BAG ON ANGEL DUST.

01:51.510 --> 01:53.535
COME ON, DUDE,
I WAS IN THE ZONE!

01:53.580 --> 01:56.674
NOW I HAVE TO START
ALL OVER.
[phone rings]

01:57.950 --> 02:00.771
(Gus)
SHAWN, THE FLOOR IS FLAT.

02:00.820 --> 02:03.448
I DON'T KNOW WHY YOU CAN'T
JUST PUTI' IN OUR OFFICE.

02:03.490 --> 02:06.414
BECAUSE, GUS, ANYONE CAN HIT
A BALL INTO AN EMPTY CUP.

02:06.460 --> 02:08.257
THE TRUE CHALLENGE
IS TO GUIDE THE BALL

02:08.290 --> 02:10.451
ALMOST MAGICALLY
THROUGH THE ORGANIZED CHAOS

02:10.490 --> 02:11.718
OF HUMAN BUSTLE

02:11.760 --> 02:13.921
AND INTO THE HOLE
AS IF NO ONE WERE THERE.

02:13.960 --> 02:15.518
LET'S JUST HOPE IT WORKS BETTER
THAN WHEN YOU ATTEMPTED

02:15.560 --> 02:16.822
THE SAME THING WITH THE DARTS.

02:16.870 --> 02:19.293
PARDON ME? I NAILED THAT.
30-FOOT BULL'S-EYE.

02:19.340 --> 02:20.693
NO. YOU HIT A GUY'S EYE.

02:20.740 --> 02:23.208
SHH.

02:35.280 --> 02:36.281
DUDE!

02:41.620 --> 02:42.621
STAY ALIVE.

02:43.630 --> 02:45.518
GET THERE.

02:45.560 --> 02:46.527
OH!

02:46.560 --> 02:47.527
HOW ABOUT MY PHONE CALL?

02:47.560 --> 02:49.266
YOU'LL GET
YOUR PHONE CALL.

02:49.300 --> 02:50.597
I DIDN'T DO IT.
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME.

02:57.610 --> 02:58.634
OH!

02:58.670 --> 02:59.773
WHO PUT A PUTTING GREEN
IN HERE?

02:59.810 --> 03:01.232
HE WAS ALREADY DEAD.

03:01.280 --> 03:03.475
I WAS TRYING
TO RESUSCITATE HIM.

03:03.510 --> 03:04.704
WAIT, WAIT, THAT GUY.

03:04.750 --> 03:05.944
THE ONE WITH THE GREAT HAIR.

03:05.980 --> 03:07.174
HE CAN VOUCH FOR ME.

03:07.220 --> 03:08.778
I THINK WE WORKED AT BUSCH
GARDENS TOGETHER ONE SUMMER.

03:08.820 --> 03:10.811
YEAH, WE MADE FUNNEL CAKES.

03:10.850 --> 03:11.817
OH, LOOK AT THAT, GUS.

03:11.850 --> 03:12.851
HE MUST'VE GO'ITEN ME
CONFUSED

03:12.890 --> 03:14.312
WITH ANOTHER MAN
WITH GREAT HAIR.

03:14.360 --> 03:16.282
AND THE WHITE GUY.
I KNOW HIM TOO.

03:16.330 --> 03:17.786
SAVE IT, RYAN.
HEY, REMEMBER--

03:17.830 --> 03:18.979
JUST SHUT UP.

03:19.030 --> 03:20.554
UH, JULES.

03:21.930 --> 03:24.296
WHAT'S THE STORY THERE?
YEAH.

03:24.330 --> 03:25.558
THAT'S RYAN BAINSWORTH,

03:25.600 --> 03:27.568
OR "LYIN' RYAN" AS WE CALL HIM
AROUND HERE.

03:27.600 --> 03:29.807
HE'S A COMPULSIVE LIAR
WHO IS NOTORIOUS

03:29.840 --> 03:31.660
FOR CALLING IN TIPS
AND SENDING THE DEPARTMENT

03:31.710 --> 03:33.337
ON WILD GOOSE CHASES.

03:33.380 --> 03:35.405
HE'S PRETTY MUCH
AN EMBARRASSMENT TO ALL OF US.

03:35.440 --> 03:37.249
HOW CAN YOU TELL THAT SOMEONE'S
A COMPULSIVE LIAR?

03:37.280 --> 03:39.248
I MEAN, ASSUMING THAT
THEIR PANTS AREN'T ON FIRE?

03:39.280 --> 03:40.747
TRUST ME. WE KNOW.

03:40.780 --> 03:41.678
OH, COME ON, JULES.

03:41.720 --> 03:43.608
WE ALL TEND TO BEND THE TRUTH
JUST A LITTLE.

03:43.650 --> 03:45.584
NOT ME. MM-MM.
OH REALLY?

03:45.620 --> 03:46.552
DOES THIS RING A BELL?

03:46.590 --> 03:48.410
[high pitched voice]
NO, SHAWN, I HAVE NOT HAD

03:48.460 --> 03:50.348
ANY NAUGHTY DREAMS
ABOUT YOU.

03:50.390 --> 03:51.584
[normal voice]
AND...

03:51.630 --> 03:54.326
[high pitched voice]
YES, SHAWN, I DO WISH
GUS WAS NEVER BORN

03:54.360 --> 03:55.850
SO THAT I COULD BE
YOUR PARTNER.

03:55.900 --> 03:57.527
WHAT? THAT'S MESSED UP.
TRUE STORY.

03:57.570 --> 03:58.628
I NEVER SAID THAT, GUS.

04:00.300 --> 04:02.404
ANYWAY,
RYAN USUALLY COMES IN

04:02.440 --> 04:04.260
CLAIMING TO BE A WITNESS
TO A CRIME.

04:04.310 --> 04:06.631
BUT THIS TIME,
LOOKS LIKE HE'S COMMITTED ONE.

04:11.380 --> 04:12.870
OH, DETECTIVE O'HARA,

04:12.920 --> 04:13.875
THIS IS DR. MOREY,

04:13.920 --> 04:14.978
THE D.A.'S
PSYCHOLOGICAL EXPERT.

04:15.020 --> 04:17.318
NICE TO MEET YOU.
HERE'S THE FILE ON OUR SUSPECT.

04:17.350 --> 04:18.988
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

04:19.020 --> 04:20.317
DON'T MIND THEM.

04:20.360 --> 04:22.351
THEY'RE JUST HERE
TO OBSERVE.

04:22.390 --> 04:23.379
SHE'S RIGHT.
PLEASE CARRY ON.

04:23.430 --> 04:24.681
BUT WHEN YOU'RE FINISHED,

04:24.730 --> 04:26.595
I'D APPRECIATE
IF YOU EVALUATE MY PARTNER GUS.

04:26.630 --> 04:28.723
FOR YEARS, HE'S
BEEN CLAIMING TO BE INSANE

04:28.760 --> 04:30.398
IN THE MEMBRANE.

04:31.630 --> 04:34.736
ALL RIGHT, WHY DON'T YOU
JUST DO US ALL A FAVOR

04:34.770 --> 04:36.362
AND WRITE DOWN IN NEAT
LITTLE LETTERS

04:36.410 --> 04:38.560
ALL ABOUT HOW YOU STABBED
AND MURDERED YOUR SUPER

04:38.610 --> 04:39.736
IN COLD BLOOD.

04:39.780 --> 04:43.079
FOR THE LAST TIME,
I'M INNOCENT.

04:43.110 --> 04:45.749
I HAD ASKED MY SUPER
TO FIX THE GARBAGE DISPOSAL.

04:45.780 --> 04:47.475
I CLOGGED IT
WITH CINNAMON STICKS

04:47.520 --> 04:49.488
AND LEMON WEDGES
FROM A MARINADE.

04:49.520 --> 04:51.078
AI-TERWARDS, HE
WAS TO CHECK MY PIPES

04:51.120 --> 04:52.917
BECAUSE THE POLARITY
IS COMPLETELY OFF

04:52.960 --> 04:55.087
AND THE WATER
DRAINS COUNTERCLOCKWISE.

04:55.120 --> 04:57.429
BUT BY THE TIME
I GOT HOME,

04:57.460 --> 04:59.724
I FOUND HIM THERE...DEAD.

04:59.760 --> 05:02.058
DOCTOR, IF I CAN SPEAK
FOR YOU...

05:02.100 --> 05:04.694
I'D RATHER YOU DIDN'T.

05:04.730 --> 05:06.027
LOOK,
ALL THINGS BEING EQUAL,

05:06.070 --> 05:07.492
I'D RATHER BE SCRAPBOOKING
RIGHT NOW.

05:07.540 --> 05:10.429
BUT THAT'S--
THAT'S NOT IMPORTANT.

05:10.470 --> 05:12.973
THOUGH I HAVE BEEN KNOWN
TO MAKE A KICK-ASS COLLAGE.

05:13.010 --> 05:14.773
THEN MAYBE YOU'D LIKE
TO TELL ME WHO DID KILL HIM.

05:14.810 --> 05:16.846
YES. AN ASSASSIN.

05:16.880 --> 05:17.847
AN ASSASSIN.

05:17.880 --> 05:19.677
A HIRED ASSASSIN.

05:19.720 --> 05:20.744
NO, TWO OF THEM, ACTUALLY.

05:20.780 --> 05:22.441
YES, YOU SEE,
THAT HAS TO BE IT.

05:22.490 --> 05:24.014
THE NIGHT BEFORE,
I WENT TO THIS RESTAURANT

05:24.050 --> 05:25.347
TO GET A BASKET
OF THESE THINGS

05:29.830 --> 05:31.127
YOU KNOW, THE ONES
WHERE THEY INJECT POTATOES

05:31.160 --> 05:32.821
WITH THE FOUR CHEESE MIXTURE,

05:32.860 --> 05:34.122
FRY THEM THREE QUARTERS
OF THE WAY,

05:34.160 --> 05:36.128
PULL THEM OUT, BATTER THEM,
FRY THEM AGAIN,

05:36.160 --> 05:38.867
AND THEN SERVE THEM WITH BACON
AND AN ANCHO CHILE SOUR CREAM.

05:38.900 --> 05:41.460
ANYWAY,
AS I WAS SITTING THERE,

05:41.500 --> 05:43.434
A CAR SPEEDS RIGHT THROUGH
THE STOREFRONT

05:43.470 --> 05:45.438
ACROSS THE STREET.

05:45.470 --> 05:47.836
IT MAKES SUCH A LOUD NOISE,
I HAD TO TURN MY HEAD AND LOOK.

05:47.880 --> 05:49.438
AND THAT IS WHEN I OVERHEARD

05:49.480 --> 05:51.505
THE GUY WITH THE CURLY-Q'S
ON HIS FACE

05:51.550 --> 05:53.768
TELL THE OTHER GUY
AT THE CORNER TABLE

05:53.820 --> 05:57.142
ABOUT THE ASSASSINATION PLOT.

05:57.190 --> 05:59.579
CAN IT BE TRUE?
NO WAY.

05:59.620 --> 06:00.655
I MEAN,
I--IS IT EVEN POSSIBLE?

06:00.690 --> 06:02.578
I COULDN'T IMAGINE.

06:02.630 --> 06:04.689
THERE'S NO WAY YOU COULD PREPARE
A FRY LIKE THAT.

06:04.730 --> 06:05.719
THAT'D BE WAY TOO MUCH
FOR TH E--

06:05.760 --> 06:07.057
FOR THE HUMAN PALATE
TO MANAGE.

06:07.100 --> 06:09.398
IT WOULD BE
A FLAVOR SEIZURE.

06:09.430 --> 06:11.421
GENTLEMEN,
PLEASE DON'T BE RIDICULOUS.

06:11.470 --> 06:12.539
SHE'S RIGHT.

06:12.570 --> 06:15.391
LET'S JUST TAKE A MINUTE HERE
TO THINK THINGS THROUGH.

06:15.440 --> 06:19.399
THEY MUST BE PARBOILING
THE POTATO FIRST.

06:19.440 --> 06:20.839
AN ASSASSINATION PLOT?

06:20.880 --> 06:22.677
SERIOUSLY, HOW GULLIBLE
DO YOU THINK WE ARE?

06:22.710 --> 06:25.702
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME.
I'M 100% SURE ON THIS.

06:25.750 --> 06:27.775
I CLEARLY HEARD
ONE OF THEM SAY

06:27.820 --> 06:31.711
THAT THEY WERE GONNA KILL
SOMEONE WITH HIS BELT BUCKLE.

06:33.190 --> 06:34.612
RYAN, COME ON.

06:34.660 --> 06:36.423
THEY MUST'VE KNOWN
THAT I OVERHEARD THEM.

06:36.460 --> 06:38.428
THAT'S WHY THEY
WERE TRYING TO KILL ME.

06:38.460 --> 06:39.449
BUT THEY SURPRISED THE SUPER
IN MY APARTMENT,

06:39.500 --> 06:41.491
GOT HIM INSTEAD.

06:41.530 --> 06:42.497
AND--AND HE TRIED
TO STOP THEM.

06:42.530 --> 06:43.667
THEY KILLED HIM.

06:43.700 --> 06:46.430
HOW DID THEY KNOW
WHERE TO FIND YOU, HUH?

06:46.470 --> 06:48.563
BECAUSE I WAS LOOKING
FOR THEM.

06:48.600 --> 06:51.603
I WAS ASKING AROUND,
PUTTING UP FLIERS.

06:51.640 --> 06:53.437
OH, FLIERS.
OH, WELL, THAT MAKES SENSE THEN.

06:53.480 --> 06:55.505
YOU ADVERTISED FOR KILLERS.

06:55.540 --> 06:56.905
(Ryan)
YOU HAVE TO BELIEVE ME.

06:56.950 --> 06:58.440
THESE ARE THE GUYS
THAT YOU WANT.

06:58.480 --> 07:00.471
IF YOU DON'T CATCH THEM,
SOMEONE ELSE IS GONNA DIE.

07:00.520 --> 07:01.748
I SWEAR TO YOU.

07:01.780 --> 07:03.042
I HAVE A QUESTION.

07:03.090 --> 07:04.489
NO.

07:04.520 --> 07:05.339
IT'S NOT
A YES OR NO QUESTION.

07:05.390 --> 07:06.140
WHAT IS
THE NAME OF THE RESTAURANT

07:06.190 --> 07:07.919
THAT SERVES
THESE ALLEGED FRIES

07:07.960 --> 07:10.781
AND MIGHT I SUBSTITUTE
A GARLIC LEMON AIOLI?

07:10.830 --> 07:12.127
SPENCER, OUT.

07:13.930 --> 07:17.058
OFFICER,
IF IT HELPS ANY,

07:17.100 --> 07:20.592
I THINK SUBSTITUTIONS
ARE ALLOWED.

07:20.640 --> 07:22.938
SO WHAT DO YOU THINK,
DR. MOREY?

07:22.970 --> 07:24.961
WELL, HE SHOWS
ALL THE CLASSIC SIGNS

07:25.010 --> 07:27.808
OF AN UNDERLYING PATHOLOGY.

07:27.840 --> 07:29.899
PEOPLE LIKE THIS LIE
IN ORDER TO MAKE

07:29.950 --> 07:30.939
THEMSELVES VALUABLE.

07:30.980 --> 07:33.073
OVER TIME,

07:33.120 --> 07:34.178
WHEN PEOPLE STOP
BELIEVING THEIR LIES,

07:34.220 --> 07:34.970
THEY'RE FORCED TO ESCALATE

07:35.020 --> 07:36.248
THEIR BEHAVIOR IN ORDER
TO RECLAIM

07:36.280 --> 07:37.781
THE ATTENTION.

07:37.820 --> 07:39.583
COULD HE ESCALATE IT
TO THE POINT OF MURDER?

07:41.560 --> 07:42.629
MY PROFESSIONAL OPINION?

07:42.660 --> 07:43.627
PLEASE.

07:43.660 --> 07:44.786
HIS POLICE HISTORY

07:44.830 --> 07:46.058
AND THE CIRCUMSTANTIAL
EVIDENCE

07:46.090 --> 07:48.058
OF HIS FINGERPRINTS
ON THE MURDER WEAPON

07:48.100 --> 07:50.728
AND THE VICTIM'S BLOOD
ON HIS HANDS...

07:50.770 --> 07:53.637
MM, YES, I THINK THAT SHOULD BE
ENOUGH TO PROSECUTE HIM.

07:53.670 --> 07:54.762
WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD.

07:54.800 --> 07:56.097
WHY?

07:56.140 --> 07:59.576
BECAUSE LYIN' RYAN
IS TELLING THE TRUTH THIS TIME.

07:59.610 --> 08:01.100
WELL...

08:05.710 --> 08:09.168
[The Friendly Indians'
I Know You Know]

08:09.220 --> 08:12.519
*

08:12.560 --> 08:15.882
* IN BETWEEN THE LINES,
THERE'S A LOT OF OBSCURITY *

08:15.920 --> 08:19.287
* I'M NOT INCLINED
TO RESIGN TO MATURITY *

08:19.330 --> 08:23.061
* IF IT'S ALL RIGHT,
THEN YOU'RE ALL WRONG *

08:23.100 --> 08:26.729
* BUT WHY BOUNCE AROUND
TO THE SAME DAMN SONG? *

08:26.770 --> 08:31.605
* YOU'D RATHER RUN
WHEN YOU CAN'T CRAWL *

08:33.240 --> 08:35.708
* I KNOW YOU KNOW

08:35.740 --> 08:37.241
* THAT I'M NOT TELLING
THE TRUTH *

08:37.280 --> 08:39.544
* I KNOW YOU KNOW

08:39.580 --> 08:40.615
* THEY JUST DON'T HAVE
ANY PROOF *

08:40.650 --> 08:41.742
* EMBRACE THE DECEPTION

08:41.780 --> 08:43.748
* LEARN HOW TO BEND

08:43.790 --> 08:45.189
* YOUR WORST INHIBITIONS

08:45.220 --> 08:48.257
* TEND TO PSYCH YOU OUT
IN THE END *

08:48.290 --> 08:54.820
* I KNOW YOU KNOW *

08:54.860 --> 08:56.828
AND YOU'RE SURE YOU WANT
TO TAKE ONE THE SBPD,

08:56.870 --> 08:58.861
AN EXPERT
IN FORENSIC PSYCHOLOGY,

08:58.900 --> 08:59.935
AND THE D.A.'S OFFICE?

08:59.970 --> 09:01.733
BECAUSE THEY ALL BELIEVE
HE'S GUILTY.

09:01.770 --> 09:02.862
I CERTAINLY
WANT TO INVESTIGATE FURTHER.

09:02.910 --> 09:06.869
EVERY GOOD LIAR'S LIES
ARE ROOTED IN A KERNEL OF TRUTH.

09:06.910 --> 09:09.879
THIS ISN'T EVEN OUR CASE.

09:09.910 --> 09:11.969
ARE YOU TRYING TO SHOW UP
THE POLICE DEPARTMENT?

09:12.010 --> 09:13.113
IS THIS ABOUT PRIDE?

09:13.150 --> 09:15.345
GUS, I GOT THESE JEANS
AT A GARAGE.

09:15.380 --> 09:17.985
NOT A GARAGE SALE.
A GARAGE.

09:18.020 --> 09:20.955
CLEARLY PRIDE IS NOT AN ISSUE
FOR ME.

09:20.990 --> 09:23.686
THIS IS ABOUT ME
NOT WANTING A MAN

09:23.730 --> 09:24.754
TO BE WRONGFULLY CONVICTED

09:24.790 --> 09:28.624
BECAUSE HE HAS A SICKNESS
THAT HE CANNOT CONTROL.

09:28.660 --> 09:30.161
PLUS, HE APPRECIATED MY HAIR.

09:30.200 --> 09:32.088
NO, HE APPRECIATED MY HAIR.

09:32.130 --> 09:33.939
HE WAS LYING.
HE'S A COMPULSIVE LIAR.

09:33.970 --> 09:35.130
THAT'S WHAT THEY DO.

09:35.170 --> 09:36.296
COME ON.
TRY TO PLAY CATCH UP.

09:36.340 --> 09:37.602
UH, WHY DON'T YOU PLAY

09:37.640 --> 09:38.959
"INVESTIGATE THIS ON YOUR OWN"?

09:39.010 --> 09:40.375
FINE.

09:40.410 --> 09:43.800
STAY HERE, WASH THE DISHES
IN THOSE RIDICULOUS GLOVES.

09:43.850 --> 09:46.876
I'M GOING TO THE RESTAURANT
THAT HE SAID HAD CHEESE-INFUSED,

09:46.920 --> 09:48.979
TWICE-BATTERED FRIES.

09:49.020 --> 09:50.282
I'LL DRIVE.

09:55.720 --> 09:57.779
THE FRIES EXIST, SHAWN.

09:57.830 --> 09:59.923
HE WAS TELLING THE TRUTH
IN A BIG WAY.

09:59.960 --> 10:02.258
THEY'RE LIKE A PYRAMID
OF SAVORY GOODNESS.

10:02.300 --> 10:05.121
LET'S JUST SIT HERE
AND LOOK AT THEM FOR AWHILE.

10:05.170 --> 10:07.365
[sniffing]

10:07.400 --> 10:10.005
DUDE, THIS FEELS LIKE
A FAMILY ESTABLISHMENT,

10:10.040 --> 10:11.064
DOESN'T IT?

10:11.110 --> 10:12.361
I'M NOT SURE TWO RUTHLESS,
HIRED GUNMEN

10:12.410 --> 10:15.174
WOULD FREQUENT
A PLACE LIKE...

10:15.210 --> 10:18.145
(Ryan's voice)
A CAR SPEEDS RIGHT THROUGH
THE STOREFRONT WINDOW

10:18.180 --> 10:19.647
ACROSS THE STREET.

10:19.680 --> 10:21.318
THAT MADE ME TURN MY HEAD.

10:21.350 --> 10:23.716
THIS.

10:23.750 --> 10:25.980
UH, 'SCUSE US.

10:26.020 --> 10:27.089
UH-HUH.

10:27.120 --> 10:28.087
DO YOU REMEMBER
IF THERE WERE TWO

10:28.120 --> 10:30.156
THREATENING-LOOKING GUYS
SITTING AT THAT TABLE

10:30.190 --> 10:32.124
IN THE CORNER YESTERDAY?

10:32.160 --> 10:33.422
OH, MY GOSH. YES.

10:33.460 --> 10:35.098
HOW'D YOU KNOW THAT?

10:35.130 --> 10:36.358
HE'S PSYCHIC.

10:36.400 --> 10:38.322
OH. OH.

10:38.370 --> 10:39.860
DO YOU DO PARTIES?

10:39.900 --> 10:40.992
PRIVATE ONES, YES.

10:41.040 --> 10:42.393
ARE YOU THINKING OF THROWING
A LITTLE SOMETHING TOGETHER

10:42.440 --> 10:43.702
FOR YOURSELF?

10:43.740 --> 10:44.809
OH, NO, MY NIECE,

10:44.840 --> 10:45.909
SHE'S TURNING SIX.

10:45.940 --> 10:47.077
NOT AVAILABLE FOR THAT.

10:47.110 --> 10:47.974
UH, DO YOU BY CHANCE

10:48.010 --> 10:49.944
