WHEN YOU ASK THAT QUESTION.

16:41.330 --> 16:42.490
THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

16:44.330 --> 16:45.365
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

16:45.400 --> 16:46.628
DAPPER DAN.

16:46.670 --> 16:48.433
