MAKE SOME NOIZE...
WITH A Z.

16:56.310 --> 16:59.438
YOU KNOW WHAT,
JUST FORGET I ASKED, OKAY?

16:59.480 --> 17:02.574
WHAT IS IT, FIRST DAY
WITH THE NEW FEET?

17:02.620 --> 17:06.386
