DIDN'T SHOW UP AGAIN.

17:09.520 --> 17:10.680
BUT HE'S RIGHT.

17:10.730 --> 17:12.584
YOU GUYS CAN'T COMMUNICATE
WITH RYAN WHILE HE'S IN CUSTODY.

17:12.630 --> 17:14.427
