AND WHERE.

18:12.350 --> 18:13.248
RYAN, THAT--THAT'S EVERYTHING
WE NEED TO KNOW.

18:13.290 --> 18:14.609
THAT'S ALL OF IT.

18:14.660 --> 18:15.718
