21:03.430 --> 21:05.455
RYAN, JUST, UH,

21:05.490 --> 21:07.629
JUST TELL HIM EXACTLY
WHAT YOU TOLD THE POLICE.

21:07.660 --> 21:10.697
OH, I KILLED THE SUPER
OF MY BUILDING.

21:10.730 --> 21:12.766
WHAT?

21:12.800 --> 21:14.495
THAT'S NOT--THAT'S NOT TRUE
AT ALL.

21:14.540 --> 21:15.996
WELL, THE SANTA BARBARA
POLICE DEPARTMENT

21:16.040 --> 21:17.530
SEEMS TO THINK IT'S TRUE.

21:17.570 --> 21:18.832
OTHERWISE, WHY DID THEY
ARREST ME?

21:18.870 --> 21:20.428
(Henry)
SHAWN, IF THIS GUY

21:20.480 --> 21:21.538
SAYS THAT HE'S GUILTY,

21:21.580 --> 21:22.535
WHAT THE HELL AM I DOING HERE?

21:22.580 --> 21:23.604
HE'S LYING.

21:23.650 --> 21:24.844
WAIT, HE'S LYING ABOUT LYING?

21:26.650 --> 21:28.971
I--RYAN, RYAN,

21:29.020 --> 21:30.487
TELL HIM ABOUT THE ASSASSINS.

21:30.520 --> 21:33.557
THE CREEPY ASSASSINS.

21:33.590 --> 21:34.750
WITH THE HANDLEBAR MUSTACHE

21:34.790 --> 21:36.382
AND THE PLOT
AND THE--

21:36.420 --> 21:37.523
AND THE COUNTERCLOCKWISE
WATER.

21:37.560 --> 21:38.527
PLEASE.

21:38.560 --> 21:39.857
ASSASSINS?

21:39.890 --> 21:41.528
COUNTERCLOCKWISE WATER?

21:41.560 --> 21:43.664
REALLY?

21:43.700 --> 21:45.065
SHAWN, IF I SAID THAT,

21:45.100 --> 21:46.829
I WOULD SOUND CRAZY.

21:46.870 --> 21:48.531
DUDE, YOU ARE CRAZY.

21:48.570 --> 21:50.458
YOU'RE--YOU'RE
WAY OFF THE RESERVATION.

21:50.510 --> 21:51.909
THAT'S WHY I'M
TRYING TO KEEP YOU OUT OF JAIL.

21:51.940 --> 21:55.569
WHEN YOU LIE, DOES THAT MAKE YOU
FEEL IMPORTANT?

21:55.610 --> 21:59.444
BECAUSE IF YOU KEEP LYING
THE WAY YOU DO,

21:59.480 --> 22:01.448
NO ONE WILL BELIEVE YOU
WHEN IT COUNTS.

22:01.480 --> 22:02.674
I WILL SLAP YOU
IN THE FACE.

22:02.720 --> 22:04.915
OH, VIOLENCE
IS NOT THE ANSWER.

22:04.950 --> 22:06.679
I WOULD SAY THAT YOU ARE
THE SECOND MOST SANE PERSON

22:06.720 --> 22:08.756
IN THIS ROOM.

22:08.790 --> 22:10.883
RYAN, WOULD YOU EXCUSE US
FOR JUST A MINUTE?

22:10.930 --> 22:14.593
OH, YEAH.

22:14.630 --> 22:16.621
DON'T WANDER OFF.

22:17.930 --> 22:18.897
ALL RIGHT, SHAWN.

22:18.930 --> 22:20.534
[sighs]

22:20.570 --> 22:22.367
WHY ARE YOU WORKIN'
SO HARD ON THIS ONE?

22:22.400 --> 22:23.537
I WORK HARD ON ALL MY CASES.

22:23.570 --> 22:24.605
I-I KNOW YOU DO.

22:24.640 --> 22:26.130
YOU WORK HARD TO HAVE FUN,
TO SHOW OFF.

22:26.170 --> 22:28.377
LOOK, I'M NOT AN IDIOT.

22:28.410 --> 22:29.434
I KNOW THIS GUY'S
GOT A SCREW LOOSE.

22:29.480 --> 22:30.708
HE'S LYING OUT HIS ASS.

22:30.750 --> 22:32.001
WHAT I DON'T UNDERSTAND

22:32.050 --> 22:33.711
IS WHY YOU'RE TAKING THIS ONE
SO SERIOUSLY.

22:37.690 --> 22:41.012
I GUESS BECAUSE NOBODY,
INCLUDING THE POLICE,

22:41.060 --> 22:42.516
BELIEVES IN HIM.

22:42.560 --> 22:44.152
I KNOW WHAT'S GOING ON HERE.

22:44.190 --> 22:45.657
OH, REALLY?
YES, I DO.

22:45.690 --> 22:47.157
SHAWN, LISTEN TO ME.

22:47.190 --> 22:48.691
YOU ARE NOT RYAN.

22:48.730 --> 22:51.961
YEAH, YOU STRETCH THE TRUTH
A LITTLE BIT SOMETIMES.

22:52.000 --> 22:53.638
AT LEAST YOU KNOW
WHERE THE LINE IS.

22:53.670 --> 22:54.864
OF COURSE I KNOW WHERE
THE LINE IS.

22:54.900 --> 22:56.128
BUT ONLY
BECAUSE OF TWO THINGS.

22:56.170 --> 22:57.330
ONE--YOU ALWAYS
HAD SOMEBODY AROUND

22:57.370 --> 22:59.634
WHO KNEW WHEN YOU WERE LYING
AND BOTHERED TO CALL YOU ON IT.

22:59.670 --> 23:00.773
WHAT'S THE SECOND THING?

23:00.810 --> 23:02.698
WELL, I'D LIKE TO SAY
THAT YOU ALWAYS HAD

23:02.740 --> 23:06.005
ENOUGH NATURAL TALENT
TO FALL BACK ON.

23:07.780 --> 23:08.769
BUT I'D BE LYING.

23:08.820 --> 23:09.969
LISTEN TO ME, KID.

23:10.020 --> 23:11.578
IF YOU EVER DRAG MY ASS
DOWN HERE AGAIN

23:11.620 --> 23:12.848
TO DO GUSTER'S JOB...

23:14.190 --> 23:17.455
I'M GONNA HIT YOU UP
WITH A CONSULTING FEE.

23:17.490 --> 23:19.788
OKAY. GOOD NIGHT, CAPTAIN.
[clicks tongue]

23:22.700 --> 23:24.065
WHAT WAS THAT?

23:24.100 --> 23:27.160
THAT WAS ME
SAVING YOUR LIFE.

23:27.200 --> 23:28.428
FROM MY DAD?

23:28.470 --> 23:29.994
WE DON'T KNOW WHO
WE CAN TRUST.

23:30.040 --> 23:31.701
WE'VE GOTTA STAY LOW.

23:31.740 --> 23:35.039
LOW. I HAVE A FACE GUY

23:35.080 --> 23:36.206
WHO CAN DISGUISE US,

23:36.240 --> 23:37.400
GET US OUT OF THE COUNTRY
IF NEED BE.

23:37.450 --> 23:40.715
HE'S--YEAH, HE'S PROBABLY
GONNA HAVE TO BREAK YOUR NOSE.

23:40.750 --> 23:44.846
BUT REMEMBER, THIS IS WHAT
YOU SIGNED UP FOR.

23:44.890 --> 23:46.118
STOP IT!

23:46.150 --> 23:47.651
WHAT?

23:47.690 --> 23:49.908
THIS IS REAL.
YOUR LIFE IS IN DANGER.

23:49.960 --> 23:52.622
OKAY? EVEN BATMAN TAKES OFF
THE CAPE AND THE COWL

23:52.660 --> 23:54.150
WHEN HE'S IN THE BAT CAVE
WITH ALFRED.

23:54.200 --> 23:55.929
SO JUST...

23:55.960 --> 23:57.769
PRETEND LIKE I'M ALFRED

23:57.800 --> 24:01.759
AND YOU BE RYAN...

24:01.800 --> 24:03.734
WAYN E.

24:03.770 --> 24:05.658
[phone rings]
AH, IT'S THEM!
IT'S THEM! DON'T GET IT!

24:05.710 --> 24:07.132
HOLD ON.
DON'T!

24:09.110 --> 24:10.771
HELLO.

24:10.810 --> 24:12.243
SHAWN, I CAN'T BELIEVE
I'M MAKING THIS CALL.

24:12.280 --> 24:14.840
BUT I FIGURED IT OUT.

24:14.880 --> 24:16.973
I'M STANDING
AT 420 MAIN STREET.

24:17.020 --> 24:18.647
AND GUESS WHAT IT IS?

24:18.690 --> 24:20.851
A HOSPITAL.

24:23.690 --> 24:25.055
SPENCER, WHAT THE HELL?

24:25.090 --> 24:26.079
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

24:26.130 --> 24:27.085
YEAH, OF COURSE
I AM. WHY?

24:27.130 --> 24:28.097
WELL,
WE GOT THE MESSAGE

24:28.130 --> 24:29.097
THAT YOU WERE
AT THE HOSPITAL.

24:29.130 --> 24:30.563
SOMETHING ABOUT LIFE
AND DEATH.

24:30.600 --> 24:32.124
OH RIGHT. THAT.

24:32.170 --> 24:33.125
WELL, WE ARE IN A HOSPITAL.

24:33.170 --> 24:34.489
AND AS IT HAPPENS,

24:34.540 --> 24:35.666
IT'S FILLED WITH BOTH LIFE
AND DEATH.

24:35.700 --> 24:36.928
I KNEW I SHOULD'VE LEI-T
THAT MESSAGE.

24:36.970 --> 24:38.267
WHAT'S GOING ON, SPENCER?

24:38.310 --> 24:39.766
RYAN AND I SPENT
SOME QUALITY TIME

24:39.810 --> 24:41.004
IN A PSYCHIC SWEAT LODGE.

24:42.280 --> 24:43.429
TOWELED.
FULLY.

24:43.480 --> 24:44.572
AND I HAVE HAD A CLEAR VISION
OF THE ABSOLUTE TRUTH.

24:44.610 --> 24:48.512
THE TARGET OF THE ASSASSINATION
IS RIGHT DOWN THE HALL.

24:48.550 --> 24:50.586
HIS NAME IS TOM.
TOM LIEBER.

24:50.620 --> 24:51.780
AND HE NEEDS
POLICE PROTECTION.

24:51.820 --> 24:53.139
THIS MORE OF YOUR BULL CRAP,
BAINSWORTH?

24:53.190 --> 24:54.612
BECAUSE IN ADDITION
TO YOUR MURDER CHARGE,

24:54.660 --> 24:55.911
I'M PRETTY SURE
WE HAVE ENOUGH TO CHARGE YOU

24:55.960 --> 24:58.520
WITH RECKLESS DISREGARD
OF POLICE RESOURCES.

24:58.560 --> 24:59.754
YOU TOO AS WELL.

24:59.790 --> 25:00.552
MORE THAN ENOUGH GROUNDS.

25:00.600 --> 25:01.828
WAIT, NO, YOU HAVE
TO BELIEVE US.

25:01.860 --> 25:03.794
(man)
YOU'RE KILLING ME.

25:03.830 --> 25:05.627
YOU'RE KILLING ME!

25:10.040 --> 25:11.029
FREEZE!

25:11.070 --> 25:12.105
[video game beeps]

25:12.140 --> 25:13.300
[video character dies]

25:13.340 --> 25:15.570
[game ends]

25:15.610 --> 25:17.305
PERFECT TIMING. I'M DEAD.

25:17.340 --> 25:28.148
THANKS A LOT.

25:28.190 --> 25:29.953
YOU. OUT.

25:29.990 --> 25:32.151
NO, NO, NO. I DON'T WANT
TO HEAR IT ANYMORE.

25:32.190 --> 25:34.192
GET OUT.

25:37.600 --> 25:38.862
SPENCER,

25:38.900 --> 25:40.697
THANK YOU ONCE AGAIN
FOR COMPLETELY WASTING MY TIME.

25:40.740 --> 25:41.536
ONCE AGAIN?

25:41.570 --> 25:42.491
JUST LAST WEEK,
I GAVE YOU THE TIP

25:42.540 --> 25:44.804
ABOUT THE TWICE YEARLY SALE
AT T.J. MAXX.

25:44.840 --> 25:47.104
RACKS AND RACKS
OF $7 TIES.

25:47.140 --> 25:48.630
WASTING YOUR TIME?
I DON'T THINK SO.

25:48.680 --> 25:49.772
WHAT'S GOIN' ON?

25:49.810 --> 25:51.107
IS THIS ABOUT THE ACCIDENT?

25:51.150 --> 25:52.845
BECAUSE I STILL
DON'T REMEMBER IT.

25:52.880 --> 25:53.949
WHAT ACCIDENT?

25:53.980 --> 25:55.117
I HIT A CAR.

25:55.150 --> 25:56.970
YOU MEAN, YOU WERE HIT
BY A CAR.

25:57.020 --> 25:58.146
NO, I HIT ONE.

25:58.190 --> 25:59.680
OR AT LEAST,
THAT'S WHAT THEY TOLD ME.

25:59.720 --> 26:00.482
I DON'T REMEMBER ANY OF IT.

26:00.520 --> 26:02.750
WHY WOULD I EVEN
WANT TO HIT A BUICK?

26:02.790 --> 26:04.758
I DON'T HAVE ANYTHING
AGAINST BUICKS.

26:04.790 --> 26:05.984
CARLTON, LOOK AT THIS.

26:07.230 --> 26:09.653
SIR, ARE YOU SUFFERING
FROM AMNESIA?

26:09.700 --> 26:11.258
YEAH. MAYBE. ITHINK.

26:11.300 --> 26:12.790
OR SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

26:12.830 --> 26:15.264
GREAT, LEAVE IT
TO LYIN' RYAN TO FIND

26:15.300 --> 26:17.165
THE ONLY AMNESIAC
IN SANTA BARBARA.

26:17.200 --> 26:19.805
ALTHOUGH I WON'T BE THE ONLY
AMNESIA PERSON MUCH LONGER.

26:19.840 --> 26:21.034
I'M GETTING MY MEMORY BACK.

26:21.080 --> 26:22.809
A LITTLE BIT EACH DAY.

26:22.840 --> 26:24.273
LOOK, LIEBER.
TOM.

26:24.310 --> 26:25.641
I NEVER FORGOT THAT.

26:25.680 --> 26:27.170
HOW WONDERFUL FOR YOU.

26:27.210 --> 26:29.019
WE THINK YOU MAY BE
IN GRAVE DANGER.

26:29.050 --> 26:31.280
NO, WE DON'T.
YES, WE DO.

26:31.320 --> 26:34.118
THIS SIDE OF THE ROOM,
THE COOL SIDE--

26:34.160 --> 26:35.718
SORRY, JULES,

26:35.760 --> 26:37.648
THINK THAT [whispers].

26:37.690 --> 26:39.851
SOMEONE MAY BE TRYING
TO KILL YOU.

26:40.860 --> 26:41.827
ARE YOU BLACKMAILING
ANYONE?

26:41.860 --> 26:43.725
ARE YOU
HAVING A TORRID AFFAIR?

26:43.770 --> 26:45.021
ARE YOU--ARE YOU PART
OF TREADSTON E?

26:45.070 --> 26:47.391
WAIT, DON'T ANSWER
THE LAST QUESTION.

26:47.430 --> 26:48.761
OH, WOW, NO. NO.

26:48.800 --> 26:49.562
I-I WORK FROM HOME.

26:49.600 --> 26:51.067
RECEIVING AND PROCESSING
COMPLAINTS

26:51.110 --> 26:52.862
FOR A MATTRESS MANUFACTURER.

26:52.910 --> 26:55.777
ON TUESDAYS, I GO OUT
AND GET NEW GAMES.

26:55.810 --> 26:57.175
MAYBE THROW IN A TRIP
TO 7-11 FOR A GRAPE SLURPEE--

26:57.210 --> 26:58.848
WHICH MUST HAVE BEEN
WHERE I WAS GOING.

26:58.880 --> 27:00.814
OH, JUST Al-TER 6:00.

27:00.850 --> 27:02.715
ANAPAMU STREET.

27:02.750 --> 27:04.411
I WOULD'VE BEEN THERE
RIGHT AFTER THE...

27:04.450 --> 27:05.815
WHAT?

27:05.850 --> 27:08.216
MY GAMES...
ALL OVER THE STREET.

27:08.260 --> 27:09.818
HOW GREAT
WOULD THOSE HAVE BEEN

27:09.860 --> 27:11.088
DURING MY CONVALESCENCE?

27:11.130 --> 27:12.757
OKAY, THIS IS FASCINATING.

27:12.790 --> 27:14.792
SPENCER,
MAKE-BELIEVE TIME'S OVER.

27:14.830 --> 27:15.956
WE GOT REAL POLICE WORK
TO DO.

27:16.000 --> 27:17.865
BY THE WAY, YOU'RE STILL
A LONG WAY'S OFF

27:17.900 --> 27:19.265
FROM CONNECTING ANYONE
OTHER THAN RYAN

27:19.300 --> 27:21.336
TO THE MURDER OF THAT SUPER.

27:21.370 --> 27:23.838
[phone rings]

27:23.870 --> 27:25.030
HEY, CHIEF.
WHAT DO YA GOT?

27:25.070 --> 27:26.139
SHAWN.

27:26.170 --> 27:27.728
WHAT ARE WE DOING?

27:27.780 --> 27:29.133
RYAN LIED TO US AGAIN.

27:29.180 --> 27:30.943
HE MADE US LOOK
LIKE FOOLS AGAIN.

27:30.980 --> 27:32.948
AND NOW WE'RE STANDING
IN A ROOM WITH A GUY

27:32.980 --> 27:35.016
WHO LITERALLY KNOWS NOTHING.

27:36.420 --> 27:37.739
NO OFFENSE, TOM.

27:37.790 --> 27:38.916
NO. NONE TAKEN.

27:38.950 --> 27:40.918
VISITING HOURS ENDED
HOURS AGO.

27:40.960 --> 27:43.349
YOU GENTLEMEN NEED TO FINISH
YOUR BUSINESS NOW.

27:43.390 --> 27:45.278
OH, OUR BUSINESS
IS DEFINITELY FINISHED.

27:45.330 --> 27:46.456
TRUST ME.

27:46.490 --> 27:49.050
TOM, I DO HOPE
YOU REMEMBER STUFF.

27:51.770 --> 27:53.362
YEAH. NO, NO.
YOU'VE GOT IT.

27:53.400 --> 27:54.469
WE'LL BE THERE IN TEN.

27:54.500 --> 27:56.434
I CERTAINLY HOPE YOU DIDN'T MAKE
DINNER RESERVATIONS

27:56.470 --> 27:57.437
AT SOUP PLANTATION.

27:57.470 --> 27:59.131
GUS AND I
HAVE ALREADY EATEN.

27:59.170 --> 28:00.330
THOUGH I SUPPOSE WE COULD GO
AROUND THE CORNER

28:00.370 --> 28:01.337
AND WATCH YOU EAT,

28:01.380 --> 28:02.335
IF YOU'D LIKE.

28:02.380 --> 28:04.075
THEY JUST FOUND A BODY
IN A VACANT OFFICE SUITE

28:04.110 --> 28:05.748
ON THE CORNER
OF GARDENER AND CARRILLO.

28:05.780 --> 28:06.849
REALLY. ANY I.D.?

28:06.880 --> 28:07.744
YOU'RE NOT
GONNA BELIEVE THIS.

28:07.780 --> 28:09.213
IT IS THE DEFENSE ATTORNEY
ON THE CASE

28:09.250 --> 28:10.945
I'VE BEEN TRYING TO GIVE
TESTIMONY ON ALL WEEK.

28:10.990 --> 28:13.185
HUH. WHAT ABOUT
RYAN'S ASSASSINS?

28:13.220 --> 28:14.380
YOU SHOULD CALL
EITHER THE LOCH NESS MONSTER

28:14.420 --> 28:15.751
OR BIGFOOT IF YOU GET
IN TROUBLE.

28:15.790 --> 28:17.758
I'M SURE THEY'D BE HAPPY
TO HELP.

28:17.790 --> 28:20.156
FIRST OF ALL, BIGFOOT AND I
HAVEN'T SPOKEN IN FIVE YEARS.

28:20.190 --> 28:21.794
SIX, IF YOU DON'T COUNT
HIS COUSIN'S WEDDING.

28:21.830 --> 28:23.092
WHICH WAS LITERALLY, LIKE,
HEY, B.

28:23.130 --> 28:25.269
[growls]

28:25.300 --> 28:26.858
COME ON, JULES.
YOU KNOW ME.

28:26.900 --> 28:27.889
AND I KNOW PEOPLE.

28:27.940 --> 28:29.760
I CAN READ THEM.
YOU KNOW THAT.

28:29.800 --> 28:32.200
I'VE SPENT ENOUGH TIME WITH RYAN
TO KNOW WHEN HE'S LYING

28:32.240 --> 28:33.366
AND WHEN HE'S TELLING
THE TRUTH.

28:33.410 --> 28:36.208
AND THERE IS A KERNEL OF TRUTH
IN EVERY ONE OF HIS STORIES.

28:36.240 --> 28:38.105
SO THEY CANNOT BE DISMISSED.

28:38.150 --> 28:40.505
NEITHER CAN HE.
HE'S A PERSON.

28:40.550 --> 28:44.486
A PERSON IS MORE THAN THE TALES
THAT THEY TELL.

28:44.520 --> 28:47.444
YEAH, WELL, RIGHT NOW,
HE'S MORE THAN JUST A PERSON.

28:47.490 --> 28:49.082
HE'S A DOCTOR.

28:49.120 --> 28:51.259
YOU KNOW, THEY SAY WE DOCTORS
HAVE A GOD COMPLEX.

28:51.290 --> 28:54.259
BUT AFTER SEVEN YEARS
OF NEUROSURGERY,

28:54.300 --> 28:56.894
I SAY WE HAVE A COMPLEX GOD.

29:00.000 --> 29:01.035
LOOK ON THE BRIGHT SIDE,
SPENCER.

29:01.070 --> 29:02.435
YOU KEEP UP
THIS LOSING STREAK,

29:02.470 --> 29:05.132
YOU WILL BECOME COMPLETELY
USELESS TO THE DEPARTMENT.

29:11.810 --> 29:13.914
I KNOW.
WE HAVEN'T EATEN.

29:13.950 --> 29:16.976
(Gus)
SHAWN, WE ARE TREADING
ON THIN ICE

29:17.020 --> 29:17.839
RIGHT NOW.

29:17.890 --> 29:19.039
YES, BUT I'M ABOUT TO DO
A DOUBLE AXEL

29:19.090 --> 29:21.979
INTO A SALCHOW AND FINISH
WITH A SWEET LITTLE CAMEL TOE.

29:22.020 --> 29:24.022
YOU MEAN CAMEL SPIN.
I'VE HEARD IT BOTH WAYS.

29:24.060 --> 29:25.220
I'M RIGHT
ABOUT THE RYAN THING.

29:25.260 --> 29:27.353
NO, YOU ARE OBSESSED
WITH THIS RYAN THING.

29:27.390 --> 29:30.154
AND, DUDE, IF YOUR PSYCHIC
POWERS DISAPPEAR,

29:30.200 --> 29:32.020
VICK WON'T NEED
TO HIRE US ANYMORE.

29:32.070 --> 29:33.025
THERE'S NO WAY
WE CAN SUBSIST

29:33.070 --> 29:34.162
ON THE PRIVATE JOBS
WE GET.

29:34.200 --> 29:35.861
HOW MANY TIMES
MUST WE GO THROUGH THIS?

29:35.900 --> 29:38.539
I AM THIS CLOSE TO GETTING
ON THE PRO BOWLERS TOUR.

29:38.570 --> 29:40.936
I AM NOT DOING THIS.

29:40.980 --> 29:42.072
OKAY, I GET IT.

29:42.110 --> 29:43.805
WE HAVE TO MAKE NICE
WITH THE CHIEF.

29:43.850 --> 29:45.579
WHY DO YOU THINK I BROUGHT
ALONG THIS PEACE OFFERING?

29:45.610 --> 29:47.043
YOU REALLY THINK
THAT ONE CONTAINER

29:47.080 --> 29:48.547
OF FRIES QUATRO QUESOS
DOS FRITOS

29:48.580 --> 29:49.877
IS GONNA FIX EVERYTHING?

29:49.920 --> 29:51.410
YES, I DO.

29:53.390 --> 29:55.017
THE LAWYER
HAD TWO SLUGS IN HIS CHEST.

29:55.060 --> 29:57.051
BALLISTICS IS CHECKING
THE SYSTEM FOR MATCHES.

29:57.090 --> 29:57.920
ANY TRACE?

29:57.960 --> 29:59.279
NOTHING YET.

29:59.330 --> 30:00.991
THE LAB'S GONNA CALL
THE SECOND THEY FIND ANYTHING.

30:01.030 --> 30:02.327
OH, NOT NOW, GENTLEMEN.

30:02.360 --> 30:04.260
WE ARE IN THE MIDDLE
OF A HOMICIDE INVESTIGATION.

30:04.300 --> 30:06.165
AND DON'T THINK I DON'T KNOW
THAT YOU'VE BEEN WASTING

30:06.200 --> 30:07.224
MY DETECTIVES' TIME

30:07.270 --> 30:10.933
CHASING LEADS ONCE AGAIN
SUPPLIED BY RYAN BAINSWORTH.

30:10.970 --> 30:13.564
CHIEF.
CHIEF VICK.
HMM?

30:13.610 --> 30:16.374
CHIEF KAREN CHARLES VICK.

30:16.410 --> 30:18.571
HERE.

30:18.610 --> 30:19.941
OOH.

30:22.250 --> 30:24.548
IT'S A FRIES QUATRO
QUESOS DOS FRITOS.

30:24.590 --> 30:25.989
AND APPARENTLY
DOESN'T TRAVEL WELL.

30:26.020 --> 30:27.317
THE POINT IS,

30:27.350 --> 30:29.454
WE ARE SORRY FOR MAKING
LASSITER AND JULIET

30:29.490 --> 30:31.924
RUN AROUND TOWN
ON WILD GOOSE CHASES.

30:31.960 --> 30:33.222
SHAWN'S PSYCHIC POWERS

30:33.260 --> 30:35.125
HAVE BEEN A TAD
ON THE FRITZ.

30:35.160 --> 30:38.061
THE GOOD NEWS IS, THEY ARE BACK
TO 100% WORKING ORDER

30:38.100 --> 30:40.989
AND WE ARE FULLY AVAILABLE
TO HELP ON THIS MURDER CASE

30:41.040 --> 30:42.928
YOU ARE NOW ON.
EVEN MORE GOOD NEWS,

30:42.970 --> 30:44.267
THOSE TASTE BETTER
THAN THEY LOOK.

30:44.310 --> 30:45.504
(Gus)
YES, THEY DO.

30:45.540 --> 30:48.008
YEAH, FINE.
APOLOGY ACCEPTED.

30:48.040 --> 30:49.928
AND MY MIDDLE NAME
IS NOT CHARLES.

30:49.980 --> 30:52.107
I TOOK A SHOT.
I KNEW IT WAS A "C."

30:53.950 --> 30:56.111
NOW, ABOUT THIS DEFENSE
ATTORNEY'S MURDER CASE,

30:56.150 --> 30:59.119
ANY VICTIM
OF AN ASSASSINATION PLOT?
WOW. REALLY?

30:59.150 --> 31:00.640
AS ODD AS IT SOUNDS,

31:00.690 --> 31:02.988
IT ACTUALLY DID CROSS
MY MIND.

31:03.020 --> 31:04.055
SO I CHECKED IT OUT.

31:04.090 --> 31:05.125
AND I CAN SAY
WITH CERTAINTY

31:05.160 --> 31:06.627
THAT HE IS NOT THE VICTIM

31:06.660 --> 31:08.594
OF MR. BAINSWORTH'S
ASSASSINATION PLOT.

31:08.630 --> 31:11.064
THE CORONER PUTS TIME OF DEATH
AT FOUR DAYS AGO.

31:11.100 --> 31:12.169
AND A RECENTLY DISCOVERED
WITNESS

31:12.200 --> 31:15.590
WHO HEARD SHOTS AT 6:00
THAT EVENING CONFIRMS IT.

31:15.640 --> 31:17.392
WHICH MEANS THE LAWYER
WAS KILLED

31:17.440 --> 31:20.534
BEFORE RYAN ALLEGEDLY OVERHEARD
THESE MEN PLANNING A HIT.

31:20.570 --> 31:22.504
OUR VICTIM WOULD'VE ALREADY
BEEN DEAD AT THAT POINT.

31:22.540 --> 31:24.178
NO NEED TO KILL HIM AGAIN.

31:24.210 --> 31:26.041
UNLESS HE WAS A ZOMBIE.

31:26.080 --> 31:27.502
(policeman)
CHIEF.
YES.

31:27.550 --> 31:29.677
THE SURVEILLANCE VIDEO
FROM THE BACK DOOR OF THE GARAGE

31:29.720 --> 31:31.017
NEAR THE SCENE OF THE CRIME
CAME IN.

31:31.050 --> 31:32.039
IT'S CORRUPTED.

31:32.090 --> 31:33.148
THERE'S NOT MUCH OF IT.

31:33.190 --> 31:34.680
HEY, ARE THOSE THE FRIES
QUATRO QUESO?

31:34.720 --> 31:35.982
YES, THEY ARE.

31:36.020 --> 31:37.578
HMM.
THEY DON'T TRAVEL WELL.

31:37.620 --> 31:39.258
(Chief Vick)
O'HARA, SET IT UP.

31:40.460 --> 31:42.257
LET'S TAKE A LOOK.

31:45.430 --> 31:46.658
[whispers]
WAIT.

31:46.700 --> 31:49.294
DUDE, SHE SAID THE LAWYER
DIED FOUR DAYS AGO.

31:49.340 --> 31:50.489
YES. IT'S OVER, SHAWN.

31:50.540 --> 31:52.167
FOUR DAYS AGO WAS TUESDAY.

31:52.210 --> 31:53.302
THAT MEANS THE LAWYER
GOT KILLED

31:53.340 --> 31:55.001
IN A BUILDING
ON GARDENER STREET

31:55.040 --> 31:56.371
ON THE SAME DAY
THAT LIEBER GOT HIT BY A CAR

31:56.410 --> 31:57.536
ON ANAPAMU.

31:57.580 --> 31:59.104
NOT JUST THE SAME DAY,
THE SAME TIME.

31:59.150 --> 32:00.572
AROUND 6:00 PM.

32:00.610 --> 32:02.146
AND THOSE STREETS
ARE ONLY TWO BLOCKS AWAY.

32:02.180 --> 32:03.613
[whispers]
RYAN, THE LAWYER, LIEBER.

32:03.650 --> 32:05.345
THEY'RE ALL CONNECTED SOMEHOW.

32:05.390 --> 32:07.688
COME ON.

32:07.720 --> 32:09.085
* FRIES *

32:16.200 --> 32:17.189
SORRY TO INTERRUPT.

32:17.230 --> 32:18.265
I JUST GOT A VERY STRONG VIBE

32:18.300 --> 32:20.063
THAT YOU'RE ABOUT
TO APOLOGIZE TO US.

32:20.100 --> 32:22.330
IN WHAT WORLD WOULD WE
EVER APOLOGIZE TO YOU?

32:22.370 --> 32:24.531
WAYNE'S. MAYBE DAVE'S.
IT'S A SMALL...

32:24.570 --> 32:25.537
SPENCER.

32:25.570 --> 32:26.502
I BELIEVE THIS DVD
WILL PROVE

32:26.540 --> 32:28.337
THAT RYAN AND I
HAVE BEEN RIGHT ALL ALONG.

32:30.580 --> 32:33.743
[static hiss]

32:33.780 --> 32:35.111
[inhales]

32:35.150 --> 32:38.119
NOW, WHO'S THAT?
O'HARA, REWIND THAT.

32:47.490 --> 32:48.627
(Gus)
NO WAY.

32:48.660 --> 32:50.127
(Lassiter)
THAT'S TOM LIEBER.

32:50.160 --> 32:51.366
THAT'S THE KID
THAT BAINSWORTH LED US TO

32:51.400 --> 32:52.765
AT THE HOSPITAL, CHIEF.

32:52.800 --> 32:55.166
AND HE'S RUNNING AWAY
FROM WHERE THE BODY WAS FOUND.

32:55.200 --> 32:56.599
WELL, I GUESS

32:56.640 --> 32:59.063
YOU WERE RIGHT,
MR. SPENCER.

32:59.110 --> 33:00.236
LIEBER MUST'VE KILLED
THE LAWYER

33:00.270 --> 33:01.237
AND THEN GOT HIT
BY THE CAR

33:01.280 --> 33:02.372
AS HE FLED THE SCENE.

33:02.410 --> 33:03.434
OOH, UH, I DON'T KNOW.

33:03.480 --> 33:05.698
THE SPIRITS ARE A LITTLE
CLOUDY ON THAT PART, CHIEF.

33:05.750 --> 33:07.172
I'M SORRY FOR THE SPIRITS,

33:07.210 --> 33:08.416
BUT WE DON'T HAVE TIME
FOR GRAY AREAS.

33:08.450 --> 33:11.180
DETECT IVES, I WANT YOU TO GET
TO THAT HOSPITAL RIGHT NOW.

33:11.220 --> 33:13.381
FROM WHAT I UNDERSTAND,
LIEBER IS REGAINING HIS MEMORY.

33:13.420 --> 33:16.059
AND THE SECOND HE REMEMBERS
WHAT HE DID, HE COULD RUN.

33:16.090 --> 33:18.081
COME ON, LET'S GO.
GOT IT.

33:21.300 --> 33:23.450
SHE KNOWS SHE'S NOT
GONNA EAT THAT.

33:23.500 --> 33:25.525
[static hisses]

33:25.570 --> 33:27.595
WHAT?
I DON'T THINK
LIEBER'S THE KILLER.

33:27.630 --> 33:30.190
I SAW SOMETHING ON THE TAPE.
HOLD ON.

33:33.570 --> 33:34.537
THERE.

33:34.580 --> 33:35.433
RIGHT THERE.

33:37.280 --> 33:39.077
HE STOPS AND LOOKS BACK
OVER HIS SHOULDER.

33:39.110 --> 33:40.077
WHY?

33:40.110 --> 33:41.475
BECAUSE SOMEONE
IS CHASING HIM.

33:48.390 --> 33:52.121
TWO CREEPY SOMEONES
TO BE EXACT.

33:52.160 --> 33:53.388
LIEBER DIDN'T KILL THE LAWYER,
BUT HE SAW WHO DID.

33:53.430 --> 33:54.624
RYAN'S ASSASSINS.

33:54.660 --> 33:56.127
THEY CHASED HIM INTO TRAFFIC,
AND THEY THOUGHT

33:56.160 --> 33:57.127
THAT WAS THE END OF IT.

33:57.160 --> 34:00.368
BUT THEN THE NEWSPAPER REPORTS
THAT HE SURVIVED,

34:00.400 --> 34:02.334
GOES INTO A COMA,
WAKES UP WITH AMNESIA.

34:02.370 --> 34:04.167
THE KILLERS THINK
THEY STILL HAVE A WINDOW.

34:04.210 --> 34:08.328
BUT TODAY'S PAPER SAID
HE'S REGAINING HIS MEMORY.

34:08.380 --> 34:10.268
SO RYAN OVERHEARD
THE REAL KILLERS

34:10.310 --> 34:11.743
PLOTTING TO TAKE OUT LIEBER.

34:11.780 --> 34:13.270
WE HAVE GOT TO GET BACK
TO THE HOSPITAL

34:13.310 --> 34:14.538
AND TELL LASSIE AND JULES

34:14.580 --> 34:16.844
THAT THESE GUYS ARE COMIN' BACK
TO CLEAN UP THEIR OWN MESS.

34:16.880 --> 34:18.211
COME ON!

34:25.560 --> 34:27.755
YEAH, DOBSON, I NEED
AN A.P.B. OUT

34:27.790 --> 34:29.291
ON A THOMAS LIEBER.

34:29.330 --> 34:30.399
HE'S WANTED FOR QUESTIONING
IN A MURDER.

34:30.430 --> 34:32.227
GET HIS PICTURE
FROM THE DMV.
WHERE'S LIEBER?

34:32.270 --> 34:33.589
GONE. LOOKS LIKE
HE'S ON THE LAM.

34:33.630 --> 34:35.234
HE'S ON A LAMB,
HE WON'T GET FAR.

34:35.270 --> 34:37.568
ALPACA, DIFFERENT STORY.
THOSE THINGS REALLY FLY.

34:37.600 --> 34:38.703
YOU TWO DON'T NEED
TO BE HERE.

34:38.740 --> 34:39.707
IT'S NOT TRUE, LASSIE.

34:39.740 --> 34:41.173
LIEBER DIDN'T KILL
THE LAWYER.

34:41.210 --> 34:43.201
HE WITNESSED RYAN'S ASSASSINS
DO THE DEED,

34:43.240 --> 34:45.140
AND NOW THEY'VE
CLEARLY COME BACK TO GET HIM.

34:45.180 --> 34:46.306
AND I PROMISE I WILL ASK

34:46.350 --> 34:47.578
ALL ABOUT YOUR INSANE
LITTLE THEORIES

34:47.610 --> 34:49.248
ONCE I PUT THEM BOTH
IN JAIL.

34:49.280 --> 34:50.542
[scoffs]

34:50.580 --> 34:52.343
COME ON, GUS.
LET'S FIND TOM.

34:54.360 --> 34:57.284
I SHOULD'VE BEEN ON TO THIS
WAY EARLIER.

34:57.320 --> 34:58.218
I CAN'T BELIEVE
I DIDN'T MAKE THE CONNECTION.

34:58.260 --> 34:59.750
WE DON'T KNOW
THAT LIEBER'S DEAD, SHAWN.

34:59.790 --> 35:00.825
MAYBE HE REMEMBERED
AND LEI-T

35:00.860 --> 35:02.327
BEFORE THE KILLERS
COULD FIND HIM.

35:03.830 --> 35:05.263
HEY, GUYS.

35:05.300 --> 35:06.665
THEY'RE RIGHT BEHIND US.
THEY'RE GONNA KILL US.

35:06.700 --> 35:08.668
DRIVE. DRIVE.

35:08.700 --> 35:11.203
OKAY, ENOUGH WITH THE SEATBELTS.
JUST--LET'S GO!

35:11.240 --> 35:13.401
JUST DRIVE!
THEY'RE RIGHT BEHIND US!

35:13.440 --> 35:21.245
[car horn honks]

35:21.280 --> 35:22.611
[tires screeching]

35:26.450 --> 35:27.849
WHERE'D YOU
LEARN TO DRIVE!?

35:27.890 --> 35:29.812
ALL RIGHT, NOW,
WANNA KEEP THIS UPRIGHT.

35:29.860 --> 35:31.179
(Ryan)
I'M SORRY.

35:31.230 --> 35:32.527
I HAD TO TAKE MATTERS
INTO MY OWN HANDS.

35:32.560 --> 35:34.198
I SNUCK LIEBER
OUT THE AMBULANCE BAY.

35:34.230 --> 35:35.299
AND WHEN I SAW YOU GUYS
PULL UP,

35:35.330 --> 35:36.649
I KNEW WE COULD HIDE
IN THE CAR.

35:36.700 --> 35:38.258
INCOMING!

35:38.300 --> 35:40.666
[tires screech]

35:40.700 --> 35:42.236
[car horn honks]

35:45.840 --> 35:48.206
[car horn honks]

35:51.980 --> 35:53.845
[tires screech]

35:53.880 --> 35:55.939
SO WAIT. YOU JUST TOOK HIM
OUT OF THE HOSPITAL?

35:55.980 --> 35:57.470
WELL, I HAD TO ACT QUICKLY.

35:57.520 --> 35:59.249
TOM STARTED TO REMEMBER
EVERYTHING.

35:59.290 --> 36:01.611
WELL, NOT EVERYTHING REALLY.
YET.

36:01.660 --> 36:02.911
(Ryan)
AND THE KILLERS.

36:02.960 --> 36:04.188
THE KILLERS WERE ALREADY
IN THE BUILDING.

36:04.230 --> 36:05.481
IT WAS LIKE A GAME
OF CAT AND MOUSE

36:05.530 --> 36:07.885
TRYING TO GET OUT OF THERE
UNSEEN.

36:07.930 --> 36:09.750
[Gus and Spencer scream]

36:09.800 --> 36:11.791
[car horn honks]

36:11.830 --> 36:13.297
DIDN'T WE JUST USE
THE ELEVATOR?

36:13.330 --> 36:15.537
WOULD YOU PLEASE
LET ME TELL THE STORY?

36:15.570 --> 36:16.867
PARKING. HE'S PARKING.
HE'S PARKING!

36:16.900 --> 36:18.333
[tires screech]

36:20.770 --> 36:21.930
[tires screech]

36:21.980 --> 36:24.403
[car horn honking]

36:24.450 --> 36:26.702
VERY NICE, PARTNER.

36:26.750 --> 36:28.445
YOU JUST WEAVED YOUR WAY
THROUGH THOSE OBSTACLES

36:28.480 --> 36:32.348
LIKE A FERRET
ON ROLLER SKATES.

36:32.390 --> 36:33.846
HEY, WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

36:36.260 --> 36:38.319
WHY ARE WE SLOWING DOWN?

36:38.360 --> 36:39.384
NO, NO, NO.

36:39.430 --> 36:40.488
GUS.

36:43.600 --> 36:44.862
WHAT--WHAT--WHAT
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

36:44.900 --> 36:46.367
DUDE, THE KILLERS
ARE RIGHT BEHIND US.

36:46.400 --> 36:48.937
NOBODY'S FOLLOWING US, SHAWN,
AND THERE NEVER WAS.

36:48.970 --> 36:50.289
THE ONLY THING I KNOW
FOR SURE RIGHT NOW

36:50.340 --> 36:51.967
IS THAT WE ARE HARBORING
TWO FUGITIVES.

36:52.010 --> 36:53.261
OKAY, GUS, LOOK,
I BELIEVE RYAN,

36:53.310 --> 36:55.005
BUT I-I UNDERSTAND
WHY YOU DON'T.

36:55.040 --> 36:57.304
I'VE MAXED YOU OUT
IN THE BLIND FAITH DEPARTMENT.

36:57.340 --> 36:59.240
AND THAT'S FAIR. SO YOU DON'T
HAVE TO BELIEVE HIM.

36:59.280 --> 37:00.838
JUST KEEP BELIEVING IN ME.

37:00.880 --> 37:02.973
COME ON, BUDDY.

37:07.690 --> 37:09.988
[tires screech]

37:10.020 --> 37:11.282
(Shawn)
WHOA!

37:11.330 --> 37:12.354
(Ryan)
THAT'S THEM!

37:12.390 --> 37:13.618
THAT'S THEM!
THAT'S THEM!

37:13.660 --> 37:15.321
THAT'S THE GUYS
FROM THE RESTAURANT!

37:15.360 --> 37:15.951
IT'S COMIN' BACK TO ME.

37:16.000 --> 37:18.889
THEY SHOT THAT MAN.

37:18.930 --> 37:20.761
[gunshot]
(Ryan)
DRIVE, DRIVE!

37:20.800 --> 37:22.461
[tires screech]

37:24.610 --> 37:26.237
[gunshot]

37:37.050 --> 37:38.540
[gunshot]

37:42.160 --> 37:43.809
(Shawn)
WE GOTTA GET OUTTA HERE!
WE'RE SITTING DUCKS!

37:43.860 --> 37:44.827
GET OUTTA THE CAR,
COME ON!

37:44.860 --> 37:47.055
[all shouting at once]

37:47.090 --> 37:48.591
[gunshots]

37:48.630 --> 37:50.757
OW! GLASS!
WATCH YOUR EYES!

37:50.800 --> 37:52.893
RUN, RUN, RUN, RUN!
GO, GO! RUN, RUN!

37:52.930 --> 37:54.067
[gunshot]
SERPENTINE! SERPENTINE!

37:54.100 --> 37:55.067
ZIG ZAG!

37:55.100 --> 37:56.761
GO! HIDE IN HERE!

37:58.770 --> 38:00.806
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?
WE'RE NEVER GONNA MAKE IT!

38:00.840 --> 38:02.478
NOT AT A COMPLETE STOP,
WE WON'T.

38:02.510 --> 38:03.636
(Lieber)
DOCTOR, THIS BAG IS EMPTY.

38:03.680 --> 38:04.806
IS THAT IMPORTANT?
I'LL HOLD HIM OFF.

38:04.850 --> 38:05.703
GET HIM BACK
TO THE HOSPITAL.

38:05.750 --> 38:07.308
HOPEFULLY LASSIE AND JULES
ARE STILL THERE.

38:07.350 --> 38:08.840
HOLD 'EM OFF? HOW?
I DON'T KNOW.

38:08.880 --> 38:10.472
I'LL THINK OF SOMETHING.
I ALWAYS DO.
SO DO I.

38:10.520 --> 38:11.942
SHAWN.
JUST GET HIM OUT OF HERE!

38:11.990 --> 38:13.048
HE'S THE ONE THAT HAS
TO MAKE IT.

38:13.090 --> 38:14.387
I'M GONNA KILL YOU, SHAWN.

38:14.420 --> 38:15.387
I'LL GIVE YOU
EVERY OPPORTUNITY

38:15.420 --> 38:16.387
TO DO THAT, BUDDY.

38:16.420 --> 38:17.956
[gunshots]

38:17.990 --> 38:19.480
GOD.

38:27.830 --> 38:29.969
WE ACCEPT THE TERMS
OF YOUR SURRENDER.

38:30.000 --> 38:31.558
UH, YOU MEAN
YOU'RE SURRENDERING.

38:31.610 --> 38:33.601
YEAH. WE'RE THE ONES
HOLDIN' THE GUNS HERE.

38:33.640 --> 38:36.575
[laughs]
WELL,
YOU AND THE 20 OR SO COPS

38:36.610 --> 38:38.032
THAT ARE WAITING IN LIE
AROUND THAT CORNER.

38:38.080 --> 38:40.071
PLUS, HASN'T THERE BEEN
ENOUGH BLOODSHED ALREADY?

38:40.110 --> 38:41.577
I MEAN,
FIRST THE LAWYER,

38:41.620 --> 38:43.349
THEN RYAN'S POOR SUPER.

38:43.380 --> 38:45.416
YOU GUYS ARE TERRIBLE
AT CLEANING UP Al-TER YOURSELVES.

38:45.450 --> 38:47.589
YEAH? AND YOU'RE LYING
ABOUT THE BACKUP.

38:47.620 --> 38:50.054
LOOK INTO MY EYES...

38:50.090 --> 38:52.786
AND TELL ME IF I'M LYING.

39:05.470 --> 39:06.437
[exhales]

39:06.470 --> 39:08.062
THERE'S NO BACKUP.

39:08.110 --> 39:09.077
YAH!

39:09.110 --> 39:11.408
[gunshots]

39:11.450 --> 39:15.443
[police siren blares]

39:17.420 --> 39:18.785
THEY WERE TELLING THE TRUTH?

39:18.820 --> 39:20.583
APPARENTLY SO.

39:20.620 --> 39:22.383
THAT'S A GOOD LOOKIN'
HANDLEBAR.

39:23.520 --> 39:24.987
WONDER WHO
HIS MUSTACHE GUY IS.

39:25.990 --> 39:27.480
DOWN ON THE GROUND, COWBOY.

39:28.830 --> 39:35.759
THAT'S BETTER.

39:35.800 --> 39:38.064
AH, GOOD.
YOU'RE BOTH HERE.

39:38.100 --> 39:39.135
WHOA.
LET ME GUESS.

39:39.170 --> 39:40.933
THERE'S A BOMB ON A BUS.

39:40.970 --> 39:42.403
AND--AND--AND IF IT GOES

39:42.440 --> 39:43.475
BELOW 50 MILES PER HOUR,

39:43.510 --> 39:44.647
THE WHOLE THING'S
GONNA EXPLODE.

39:44.680 --> 39:46.500
NO, NO. NO MORE LIES.

39:46.550 --> 39:48.415
I AM QUITTIN' COLD TURKEY.

39:48.450 --> 39:49.747
TURNIN' OVER A NEW LEAF.

39:49.780 --> 39:51.816
REALLY...

39:51.850 --> 39:53.044
NO MORE LYIN' RYAN.
NO.

39:53.090 --> 39:54.079
JUST LIKE YOU SAID,

39:54.120 --> 39:55.553
I AM GONNA BE JUST RYAN.

39:55.590 --> 39:57.057
IF YOU HADN'T BELIEVED ME,

39:57.090 --> 39:59.081
AN INNOCENT PERSON
WOULD HAVE ENDED UP DEAD.

39:59.130 --> 40:00.552
AND ALL BECAUSE
I BECAME A GUY

40:00.590 --> 40:01.921
WHO COULDN'T BE TAKEN
AT HIS WORD.

40:01.960 --> 40:03.655
SO I JUST WANTED TO COME HERE
TO THANK YOU

40:03.700 --> 40:04.962
BEFORE I TOOK OFF.

40:05.000 --> 40:07.560
WELL, IF IT'S ANY CONSOLATION,

40:07.600 --> 40:09.090
I BELIEVED YOU
FROM THE VERY BEGINNING.

40:09.140 --> 40:11.961
ESPECIALLY SINCE YOU RECOGNIZED
I HAVE GREAT HAIR.

40:12.010 --> 40:13.136
I WAS TALKING ABOUT HIM.

40:13.170 --> 40:14.432
YOU WERE LYING.

40:14.480 --> 40:15.902
IT'S OKAY. I FORGIVE YOU.

40:15.940 --> 40:17.168
I'M COMIN' AROUND.

40:17.210 --> 40:19.770
SO WHERE ARE YOU OFF TO?

40:19.810 --> 40:21.072
THIS IS UNBELIEVABLE.

40:21.110 --> 40:23.078
I GOT TAPPED TO CAPTAIN
A HOT AIR BALLOON

40:23.120 --> 40:24.178
IN A MULTISTATE REGATTA.

40:24.220 --> 40:25.778
I TAKE OFF TOMORROW.

40:25.820 --> 40:26.912
HOT AIR BALLOONS
HAVE CAPTAINS?

40:26.950 --> 40:28.144
OH, YEAH, OF COURSE
THEY HAVE CAPTAINS.

40:28.190 --> 40:29.179
CAPTAINS, FIRST MATES,

40:29.220 --> 40:30.915
DECKHAN DS.

40:30.960 --> 40:31.927
I GOT REALLY LUCKY.

40:31.960 --> 40:33.120
IT WAS A FRIEND OF A FRIEND
OF MINE KINDA THING.

40:33.160 --> 40:34.491
IF YOU GUYS EVER WANT
TO RIDE,

40:34.530 --> 40:35.554
I MEAN, COME ON,

40:35.600 --> 40:36.624
I OWE YOU.

40:36.660 --> 40:38.025
I'LL EVEN LET YOU STEER
THE THING.

40:38.060 --> 40:41.097
JUST DON'T TELL ANYONE, OKAY?

40:41.130 --> 40:43.690
TAKE CARE OF YOURSELVES.

40:43.740 --> 40:46.766
MAN, I AM GLAD HE IS
OUT OF OUR LIFE.

40:46.810 --> 40:49.904
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.
HOT AIR BALLOON?

40:49.940 --> 40:51.202
IT'S CRAZY THOUGH, RIGHT?

40:51.240 --> 40:54.573
YEAH, IT'S NOT POSSIBLE.

40:54.620 --> 40:57.145
THINK HE WOULD
REALLY LET US STEER?
THERE'S ONLY ONE WAY
TO FIND OUT.

40:57.180 --> 40:58.818
YOU SAID YOU WEREN'T GONNA FALL
FOR ANY MORE OF HIS STORIES.

40:58.850 --> 41:00.044
NO, I DIDN'T.
WHATEVER.
I KNEW YOU WERE LYING.

41:00.090 --> 41:01.751
YOU'RE A LIAR.
HOW AM I A LIAR?

41:01.790 --> 41:03.781
SHOTGUN.
YOU CAN'T CALL SHOTGUN
ON A HOT AIR BALLOON, SHAWN!
